<                     }

>         Scope (\_SB.PEP0)
>         {
>             Method (PEMD, 0, NotSerialized)
>             {
>                 If ((\_SB.SDFE == 0x88))
>                 {
>                     If ((\_SB.SIDV < 0x00020000))
>                     {
>                         Name (CX6, Package (0x02)
>                         {
>                             "NPARESOURCE", 
>                             Package (0x04)
>                             {
>                                 One, 
>                                 "/arc/client/rail_cx", 
>                                 0x80, 
>                                 "SUPPRESSIBLE"
>                             }
>                         })
>                         DerefOf (DerefOf (PEMC [0x12]) [0x04]) [0x03]
>                              = CX6 /* \_SB_.PEP0.PEMD.CX6_ */
>                     }
> 
>                     Return (PEMC) /* \_SB_.PEP0.PEMC */
>                 }
>                 ElseIf ((\_SB.SDFE == 0x9A))
>                 {
>                     Return (PEMX) /* \_SB_.PEP0.PEMX */
>                 }
>             }

<                 }

<                         While (One)
<                         {
<                             Name (_T_1, 0x00)  // _T_x: Emitted by ASL Compiler, x=0-9, A-Z
<                             _T_1 = ToInteger (TBID)
<                             If ((_T_1 == Zero))
<                             {
<                                 Local2 = PCG2 /* \_SB_.GPU0._ROM.PCG2 */
<                             }
<                             ElseIf ((_T_1 == 0x05))
<                             {
<                                 Local2 = PCG1 /* \_SB_.GPU0._ROM.PCG1 */
<                             }
<                             ElseIf ((_T_1 == 0x07))
<                             {
<                                 Local2 = PCG1 /* \_SB_.GPU0._ROM.PCG1 */
<                             }
<                             ElseIf ((_T_1 == 0x08))
<                             {
<                                 Local2 = PCG1 /* \_SB_.GPU0._ROM.PCG1 */
<                             }
<                             ElseIf ((_T_1 == 0x0B))
<                             {
<                                 Local2 = PCG1 /* \_SB_.GPU0._ROM.PCG1 */
<                             }
<                             ElseIf ((_T_1 == 0x0D))
<                             {
<                                 Local2 = PCG1 /* \_SB_.GPU0._ROM.PCG1 */
<                             }
<                             ElseIf ((_T_1 == 0x0F))
<                             {
<                                 Local2 = PCG1 /* \_SB_.GPU0._ROM.PCG1 */
<                             }
<                             ElseIf ((_T_1 == 0x10))
<                             {
<                                 Local2 = PCG1 /* \_SB_.GPU0._ROM.PCG1 */
<                             }
<                             Else
<                             {

---
>             Name (THRV, Zero)
>             Method (_HRV, 0, NotSerialized)  // _HRV: Hardware Revision
>             {
>                 Name (THRV, Zero)
>                 If ((\_SB.SDFE == 0x9A))
>                 {
>                     If ((\_SB.PSUB == "CRD08380"))
>                     {
>                         If ((\_SB.PLST == 0x0001000000000000))
>                         {
>                             THRV = 0x0100
>                         }
>                         Else
>                         {
>                             THRV = 0x0200
>                         }
>                     }
>                     Else
>                     {
>                         THRV = 0x0200
>                     }
>                 }
>                 ElseIf ((\_SB.SDFE == 0x88))
>                 {
>                     If (((((((\_SB.PHRV () == 0xF4) || (\_SB.PHRV () == 0x53)) || 
>                         (\_SB.PHRV () == 0x72)) || (\_SB.PHRV () == 0x85)) || (\_SB.PHRV () == 0x87)) || (\_SB.PHRV () == 0xA3)))
>                     {
>                         THRV = 0x10
>                     }
>                     Else
>                     {
>                         THRV = One
>                     }
>                 }
>                 Else
>                 {
>                     THRV = \_SB.PHRV ()
>                 }
> 
>                 Return (THRV) /* \_SB_.TZ21._HRV.THRV */
>             }
